  {
    "uuid": "8e987a1f-8408-5051-8b03-9fa84291641d",
    "entry": "検食",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "けんしょく",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "inspection of food (before it is served at a school, nursing home, etc.)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "学校給食が始まる30分前に、校長先生が異常がないか検食を行うのが毎日の決まりだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "保健所の職員が厨房に入り、保存されている食材の鮮度と検食記録を厳しくチェックした。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "検食の際は、味付けだけでなく、異物の混入や加熱不足がないかを五感で確かめる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "food sample (used to determine the source of contamination in the event of food poisoning)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "万が一の食中毒に備えて、提供した料理の検食を48時間以上冷凍保存しなければならない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "宴会場の裏側では、調理スタッフが全メニューの検食を丁寧に小分けにしてラベルを貼っている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "調査の結果、保管されていた検食から原因菌が特定され、速やかに対策が講じられた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
